																Add something here to make this feature even more compelling.
															</p>
														</section>

												</div>
												<div class="col-12">
													<ul class="actions">
														<li><a href="#" class="button large">Do Something</a></li>
														<li><a href="#" class="button alt large">Think About It</a></li>
													</ul>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
